Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:19.25,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:24.93,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:30.91,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:37.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:43.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:48.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:58.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.43,0:01:01.42,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:06.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:12.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:18.41,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.71,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.90,0:01:37.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia has told Misa of her\Nearly days with Roy Focker,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:43.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and in those memories, Misa finds\Nreflections of Hikaru and herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.19,0:01:48.99,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(94,146)}PRIVATE TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:07.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have used a little more mustard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:15.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:23.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ichijo speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Hikaru? It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:33.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I speaking with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Me! Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay? Is that you, Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been doing okay, Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:42.99,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:46.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't saved me, I would've...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\2c&HFFFFFF&\2a&H00&}Hey, it's all over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:51.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:52.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see you. Can you come to\NHighlander City right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:58.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:02:59.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I sort of made plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.17,0:03:03.60,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's a promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:05.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just change them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're meeting someone who lives\Nin Macross City, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:08.88,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.34,0:03:11.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can see them anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:13.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:18.58,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"This is Skull One.\NNothing unusual to report on patrol."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.25,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now returning to base."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:22.79,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roger. Good work, Ichijo."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks. Say, do you have any plans\Nfor your day off tomorrow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.81,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eh? No, nothing at all."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:33.20,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm flying over the forest zone right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.18,0:03:36.18,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you want, how about coming to see\Nit tomorrow? It's really beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.65,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Really?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.46,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Really. It's a promise, then.\NWe'll work out the details when I get back."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:45.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Roger! Thanks, that will be wonderful!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them anytime, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! If I just explain things,\NI'm sure they'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll come then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting. Hurry on over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I {\i1}am{\i0} a little early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:37.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:47.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't recognize you at first in that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:51.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a disguise. Anyway, hurry up\Nand come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for calling you on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:56.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the person you made plans with angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:01.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, is it all right for us to be so close?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:03.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What if some gossip columnist spots us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as I'm with you, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.62,0:05:05.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:08.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With this disguise, no one's\Ngoing to know it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you didn't recognize me at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:13.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:15.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your tie's crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got some proper clothes after all.\NTalk about a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They look good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:46.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend of my producer owns this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of celebrities come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're a full-fledged celebrity now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been for a while, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:56.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So where's your manager today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.65,0:06:00.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's out setting up some work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:11.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's wrong? He sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:20.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:21.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:23.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:27.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much, but I wanted to\Nthank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything and just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:37.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Is it true that Major Hayase and\NCaptain Ichijo are out on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:46.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the two of them are spending\Na romantic day off right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:48.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.49,0:06:50.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop being so insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.40,0:06:54.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business what\NMajor Hayase is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The less popular the girls,\Nthe more insensitive they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:06:59.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.59,0:07:03.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:04.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! I'll take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It goes great with your outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:11.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:14.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it just a little long?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That extra bit's for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:21.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How inconsiderate! You could have\Nbrought those a little later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you young people always seem\Nto be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.47,0:07:30.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To our reunion! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:42.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been since\Nwe were alone like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The last time was just after\Nthat mission, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:45.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's been around two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years... It seems short but\Nit's actually a long time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:55.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to think of it as a short\Ntime that just seems long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:58.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't feel the same\Nway you did then, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:05.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I may never see you again,\Nso I'll just say it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:09.37,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"I...loved you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just drop something\Nlike that out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:15.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, today we're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Mr. Kaifun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a job, but it's\Nright now. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:25.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!\NYou're a professional, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:30.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that any way to act?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, if this is a bad time,\NI can come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You just sit right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:45.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already! You're acting\Nlike a spoiled child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:56.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I'm all tipsy.\NThere's no way I could work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:05.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll sober you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with your games.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:12.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I've ruined your little date.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:21.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize properly later, but for now\Ndon't worry about the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bartender, another scotch and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should call it quits.\NYou've already had too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:15.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not at home either,\Nthen where could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.94,0:10:18.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was a scramble, they\Nwould've called me in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch where you're going, you\Ndumb jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was in an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.71,0:10:30.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon, military command center!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:38.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Machizaki? It's me, Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:41.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Hayase! How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:45.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing important.\NActually, it's just a personal matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:45.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:47.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Captain Ichijo is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:54.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you have a much better idea of where\NCaptain Ichijo is than I would, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With a personality like that,\Nno woman will ever fall for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:01.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\2c&HFFFFFF&\2a&H00&}They wouldn't even go out with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?! I don't see anybody\Ngoing out with {\i1}you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:06.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:12.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Misa's already gone home by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on out it's off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then could you tell me another way\Nto get to the airport?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:29.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some Zentradi on the rampage\Nat the airport right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you know, so just go on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:34.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:38.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'm not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!\NWhat do you think of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Smash some more stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't land in this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth could he be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:11.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo! I hope you realize what\Nwe had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:15.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Authorizing you to take command of this\Noperation is a very special case!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:17.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect to see that reflected\Nin your work out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:27.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Resistance will get you nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:20.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's our answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:24.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:26.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commence Operation A!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:41.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us! It's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:45.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, you idiot!\NThey're just tear-gas shells!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Earth people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.58,0:14:52.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:33.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you have things\Nwrapped up over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:38.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man... It's finally over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:50.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichijo, what should we\Ndo with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock them up in a hangar or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters will deal with them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:13.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't apologize to her today,\Nshe'll never speak to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:27.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:38.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can smell what's in there, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:52.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shane! Shane, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:00.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Shane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:17.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:36.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The forest park is closed by now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:46.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but why don't we go someplace\Nand eat these sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:50.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Something came up\Nall of a sudden, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.53,0:17:54.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, but I wish you\Nhad at least called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:56.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept calling, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:43.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrapping that around the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:51.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:57.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:18:59.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:27.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening, ladies and gentlemen\Nof South Coast City!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on receiving the\Nright of self-government
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,from the New UN Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:36.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, to celebrate your first\Nstep toward autonomy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:40.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Lynn Minmay has rushed all the\Nway here to South Coast City!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:46.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Minmay's singing embody our hopes for the\Nfuture and let's all give her a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:50.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's her old favorite,\N"My Boyfriend is a Pilot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:18.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:29.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:33.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, she's not singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.92,0:20:46.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:49.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! Minmay! Minmay! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay! Minmay! Minmay! Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Minmay! Sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:04.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to sing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.06,0:21:23.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:24.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:35.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:36.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\2c&HFFFFFF&\2a&H00&}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:54.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:59.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you showed up, Hikaru\Nand I have grown farther apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:03.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,not since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:07.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You only think of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:13.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How did your audience feel as they\Nwere going home just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:15.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:20.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your songs don't belong to you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.05,0:22:23.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to say that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:28.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When your songs have a kindness\Nthat projects concern for people's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:31.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,then you'll be a real singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:39.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,These past two years, I've worked in my own\Nway to hear those real songs of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:42.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But all that ended today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:46.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving again. I probably won't\Nsee you for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:01.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these days, let me hear a song\Nthat's filled with kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:07.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
