Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:34.81,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,455)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:43.77,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Christmas time, and news has spread\Nof Minmay's disappearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.81,0:23:48.21,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Kamujin and his men\Nhave attacked Onogi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:57.73,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.02,0:24:00.02,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"ROMANESQUE"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:02.19,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,141)}ROMANESQUE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.14,0:24:22.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:29.42,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.87,0:24:36.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:43.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:50.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.59,0:24:56.08,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.87,0:25:04.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.25,0:25:15.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
